# Claude Code session-local state (NOT the plugin manifest at .claude-plugin/)
# Use file-level patterns (not trailing /) so negation works for F9 hook files.
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.claude/skills/
# ...except the harness-repo Claude Code hooks bundle (F9) — these are tracked:
# .claude/settings.json and .claude/hooks/handler.cjs are committed intentionally.

# Impeccable live preview runtime artifacts
.impeccable-live.json
.impeccable-live/

